Shree Pushkar Chemicals & Fertilisers Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 08/11/2025 inter alia to consider and approve 1. Un-audited Standalone and Consolidated Financial Results of the Company for the Second Quarter and half year ended 30th September 2025;
2. Potential Fund raising by way of Preferential Issue and the matters incidental to it;
3. Increase in authorized share capital of the Company and consequential amendment to the capital clause in the Memorandum of association; and
4. Other Business Matters.

Shree Pushkar Chemicals & Fertilisers Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 16/05/2025 inter alia to consider and approve 1. Audited Standalone Financial Results of the Company for the fourth quarter and financial year ended 31st March 2025;
2. Audited Consolidated Financial Results of the Company for the fourth quarter and financial year ended 31st March 2025;
3. Dividend if any on Equity Shares of the Company for the financial year ended 31st March 2025; and
4. Other Business Matters.
